; preludes: form-stdlib/shared-sensing.fk
;
; shared-sensing-band — many bodies witness one field; the circle confirms; the circle teaches.
;
; A dog barks. Three bodies witness the shared field from different sensors and models:
;   "mac"   dog 88  -> SoundAnalysis, confident
;   "phone" dog 72  -> a different model, also dog
;   "watch" dog 30  -> a nascent classifier, unsure: below floor 40, contributes SILENCE not a vote
; floor 40, quorum 2. The strongest (mac) proposes "dog"; two passing bodies agree -> the circle
; CONFIRMS. The watch was too unsure to vote, yet its guess "dog" matches the circle's confirmed
; recognition -> the circle GROUNDS it: one body's truth becomes the unsure body's ground truth.
; Two control fields: a "quiet" circle (all below floor) the circle cannot confirm, and a "lone"
; circle (one body passes) it must not confirm — one body is not a circle.
;
; Verdict 127 when every claim lands:
;   1   strongest body proposes        (candidate == dog)
;   2   the circle's witnesses counted  (agree-count dog == 2)
;   4   plural witness -> confirmed      (confirmed? == 1)
;   8   the unsure body stays silent    (watch does NOT pass the floor)
;   16  the circle grounds the unsure   (watch is grounded by the confirmed recognition)
;   32  a quiet field is not confirmed  (all-below-floor -> no shared recognition)
;   64  one body is not a circle        (a lone passing body -> not confirmed)
(do
    (let circle (list
        (list "mac"   "dog" 88)
        (list "phone" "dog" 72)
        (list "watch" "dog" 30)))
    (let floor 40)
    (let quorum 2)
    (let quiet (list (list "mac" "dog" 20) (list "phone" "cat" 15)))
    (let lone  (list (list "mac" "dog" 88) (list "phone" "cat" 12)))
    (let watch (nth circle 2))
    (let c0 (if (str_eq (ss-candidate circle) "dog") 1 0))
    (let c1 (if (eq (ss-agree-count circle floor "dog") 2) 2 0))
    (let c2 (if (eq (ss-confirmed? circle floor quorum) 1) 4 0))
    (let c3 (if (ss-passes? watch floor) 0 8))
    (let c4 (if (eq (ss-grounded? watch circle floor quorum) 1) 16 0))
    (let c5 (if (eq (ss-confirmed? quiet floor quorum) 0) 32 0))
    (let c6 (if (eq (ss-confirmed? lone floor quorum) 0) 64 0))
    (add c0 (add c1 (add c2 (add c3 (add c4 (add c5 c6)))))))
